PN,32802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783691326
OL,3,CSycamore Gap sapling stolen from Lake
OL,4,CDistrict
OL,6,FThe planting of the sapling at Wray
OL,7,Fcoincided with the start of a new
OL,8,Frelationship between St Mary's Hospice
OL,9,Fand the National Trust through the
OL,10,FBranches of Care project.
OL,12,FLaura Lee, General Manager Lake
OL,13,FDistrict, Lakes & Eden Properties
OL,14,Fsaid, "We are shocked and saddened
OL,15,Fthat a sapling from the Sycamore Gap
OL,16,Ftree that was gifted to the Lake
OL,17,FDistrict National Park and planted at
OL,18,FWray in April 2026 has been stolen.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783691326
OL,3,CSycamore Gap sapling stolen from Lake
OL,4,CDistrict
OL,6,F"This tree symbolised resilience and
OL,7,Frenewal, and its loss will be deeply
OL,8,Ffelt. While this is a setback, it does
OL,9,Fnot undermine the spirit the tree
OL,10,Frepresents. Acts of care, restoration,
OL,11,Fand community support remain far
OL,12,Fstronger.
OL,14,F"We urge those involved to do the
OL,15,Fright thing, return the sapling, or
OL,16,Fcome forward. The tree belongs to
OL,17,Feveryone."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
