OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783691326
OL,3,CSycamore Gap sapling stolen from Lake
OL,4,CDistrict
OL,6,FCumbria Police are now investigating
OL,7,Fthe theft, and are asking for anyone
OL,8,Fto come forward who might have
OL,9,Finformation.
OL,11,FThe Sycamore Gap tree was deliberately
OL,12,Fcut down overnight in September 2023,
OL,13,Fprompting a national outcry and a
OL,14,Fpolice investigation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
