OL,3,CSycamore Gap sapling stolen from Lake
OL,4,CDistrict
OL,6,FLast year, Daniel Grahamm and Adam
OL,7,FCarruthers from Cumbria were found
OL,8,Fguilty of its illegal felling and were
OL,9,Fsentenced to more than four years in
OL,10,Fprison, but ITV News revealed earlier
OL,11,Fthis year that Carruthers was released
OL,12,Fearly.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
